<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/dev-plan/sec/T-003%3A%20Turborepo%20%E4%BB%BB%E5%8A%A1%E5%9B%BE%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/source_doc> "dev-plan" .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/dev-plan/sec/T-003%3A%20Turborepo%20%E4%BB%BB%E5%8A%A1%E5%9B%BE%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/content_hash> "3c35b1236904fc6765462b8bb1eadb2da0b7359a104de30f4e7322dddaef3221" .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/dev-plan/sec/T-003%3A%20Turborepo%20%E4%BB%BB%E5%8A%A1%E5%9B%BE%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/position> "000003" .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/dev-plan/sec/T-003%3A%20Turborepo%20%E4%BB%BB%E5%8A%A1%E5%9B%BE%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/narrative_body> "### T-003: Turborepo 任务图配置\n\n- **目标**: 配置 Turborepo 完整任务图（lint → typecheck → unit-test → ruleset-fixture → cross-runtime → theme-guard → visual-regression），支持远程缓存\n- **模块**: 无特定模块（工程基础）\n- **task_kind**: config\n- **tdd_acceptance**: skip\n- **priority**: P0\n- **complexity**: small\n- **sprint**: 0\n- **tdd_mode**: skip\n- **tdd_skip_reason**: \"Turborepo 任务图配置文件，无单元测试价值\"\n- **security_sensitive**: false\n- **dependencies**: [T-001]\n- **acceptance_criteria**:\n  - [ ] AC-001: Given T-003 完成，When 运行 `pnpm turbo lint typecheck`，Then Turborepo 显示任务依赖顺序（lint 先于 typecheck），无 cycle 错误\n  - [ ] AC-002: Given 运行两次 `pnpm turbo build`，When 源码未变更，Then 第二次命中 local cache，输出\"FULL TURBO\"或 cache hit 提示，构建时间显著短于首次\n- **deliverables**:\n  - [ ] `turbo.json` — 完整 pipeline 配置（`lint`, `typecheck`, `build`, `test`, `ruleset-fixture`, `cross-runtime`, `theme-guard`, `visual-regression` 任务链及 inputs/outputs 声明）\n- **relates_to**: [arch-wechat-flow#§7.4]\n- **context_load**:\n  - arch-wechat-flow#§7.4\n\n---" .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/dev-plan/sec/T-003%3A%20Turborepo%20%E4%BB%BB%E5%8A%A1%E5%9B%BE%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/Section> .
