<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/dev-plan/sec/T-044%3A%20M-008%20composeApplyZhTypo%20use%20case%20%2B%20diff%20%E9%A2%84%E8%A7%88> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/source_doc> "dev-plan" .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/dev-plan/sec/T-044%3A%20M-008%20composeApplyZhTypo%20use%20case%20%2B%20diff%20%E9%A2%84%E8%A7%88> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/content_hash> "bad35b3ce9418fe05e629f6780772c897f4eee808e8415e91f4ae5b4bbdab214" .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/dev-plan/sec/T-044%3A%20M-008%20composeApplyZhTypo%20use%20case%20%2B%20diff%20%E9%A2%84%E8%A7%88> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/position> "000003" .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/dev-plan/sec/T-044%3A%20M-008%20composeApplyZhTypo%20use%20case%20%2B%20diff%20%E9%A2%84%E8%A7%88> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/narrative_body> "### T-044: M-008 composeApplyZhTypo use case + diff 预览\n\n- **目标**: 实现 `composeApplyZhTypo` use case，产出 diff 预览（修订前后对比）和逐 rule 计数，供 UI 展示\n- **模块**: M-008 (应用层 use case)\n- **task_kind**: feature\n- **priority**: P1\n- **complexity**: medium\n- **sprint**: 5\n- **tdd_mode**: light\n- **tdd_acceptance**: all\n- **tdd_refactor**: auto\n- **security_sensitive**: false\n- **dependencies**: [T-043]\n- **acceptance_criteria**:\n  - [x] AC-001: Given `composeApplyZhTypo({ markdown: '...' })` 调用，When 执行，Then 返回 `{ fixed: '...', perRule: Record<string, number>, totalChanges: number, diff: DiffEntry[] }` [ARCH#§2.M-008]\n  - [x] AC-002: Given `diff` 字段，When 检查，Then 每个 `DiffEntry` 含 `original`（修订前文本片段）、`revised`（修订后文本片段）、`ruleId` 字段，可用于 UI 高亮展示\n  - [x] AC-003: Given `totalChanges === 0`（无需修订的文档），When `composeApplyZhTypo`，Then 返回 `{ fixed: 原始markdown, totalChanges: 0, diff: [] }`（不做不必要处理）\n- **deliverables**:\n  - [x] `packages/core/src/composers/apply-zh-typo.ts` — `composeApplyZhTypo(input: { markdown: string }) → ZhTypoComposerResult` [ARCH#§2.M-008]\n  - [x] `tests/app-layer/compose-apply-zh-typo.test.ts` — AC-001..AC-003 单元测试\n- **relates_to**: [F-014, M-008]\n- **context_load**:\n  - arch-wechat-flow-modules#§2.M-008\n  - prd-wechat-flow-f001-f014#§2.F-014\n\n---" .
