<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/arch/sec/API-007%3A%20list_marks> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/narrative_body> "#### API-007: list_marks\n\n```yaml\ntool: list_marks\nmodule: M-009\nmaps_to: F-013 AC-002 / F-003 AC-005\nrequest: {}\nresponse:\n  schema:\n    marks: { type: \"MarkSummary[]\" }\n```" .
