<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/arch/sec/API-011%3A%20describe_variant> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/narrative_body> "#### API-011: describe_variant\n\n```yaml\ntool: describe_variant\nmodule: M-009\nmaps_to: F-013 AC-002\nrequest:\n  body:\n    blockId: { type: string, required: true }\n    variantId: { type: string, required: true }\nresponse:\n  schema:\n    id: { type: string }\n    blockId: { type: string }\n    consumedTokens: { type: \"string[]\" }\n    consumedAssets: { type: \"string[]\" }\n    directiveExample: { type: string }\n```" .
