<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/test-report-wechat-flow> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/preamble_body> "# Test Report: wechat-flow\n\n[NAV]\n- §1 测试策略 → §1.1 金字塔, §1.2 IPC边界\n- §2 测试用例矩阵\n- §3 覆盖率目标\n- §4 测试环境\n- §5 测试执行结果\n- §6 缺陷清单\n- §7 结论与建议\n- §8 doc-consistency 裁决清单\n- §9 盲区登记\n[/NAV]" .
