<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/arch/sec/API-022%3A%20wechat-flow%20init> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/narrative_body> "#### API-022: wechat-flow init\n\n```yaml\ncli_command: wechat-flow init <name>\nmodule: M-011\nmaps_to: F-010 AC-003\nflags:\n  --template: { type: \"'plugin'|'theme'\", required: true, desc: \"选择脚手架骨架\" }\n  --dir: { type: string, required: false, desc: \"目标目录，缺省 ./<name>\" }\nexits:\n  0: \"成功生成骨架\"\n  1: \"目标目录非空或参数无效\"\n```" .
