<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/dev-plan/sec/T-080%3A%20M-009%20list_tokens%20/%20describe_token%20Tool%EF%BC%88thin%20wrapper%20%E2%86%92%20M-005%EF%BC%89> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/content_hash> "dcd4363f59a3bb3f63bb29b859b610e9680cb75ffb71f03c2f5368bc1ea68952" .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/dev-plan/sec/T-080%3A%20M-009%20list_tokens%20/%20describe_token%20Tool%EF%BC%88thin%20wrapper%20%E2%86%92%20M-005%EF%BC%89> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/position> "000018" .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/dev-plan/sec/T-080%3A%20M-009%20list_tokens%20/%20describe_token%20Tool%EF%BC%88thin%20wrapper%20%E2%86%92%20M-005%EF%BC%89> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/narrative_body> "### T-080: M-009 list_tokens / describe_token Tool（thin wrapper → M-005）\n\n- **目标**: MCP Tool 暴露 token 注册表（list_tokens / describe_token）；thin wrapper 调用 M-005\n- **模块**: M-009\n- **task_kind**: feature\n- **priority**: P1\n- **complexity**: small\n- **sprint**: 5\n- **tdd_mode**: light\n- **tdd_acceptance**: all\n- **tdd_refactor**: skip\n- **security_sensitive**: false\n- **dependencies**: [T-020, T-036, T-123]\n- **acceptance_criteria**:\n  - [x] AC-001: list_tokens() 返回数组长度 ≥ 60（F-003 AC-004），每项含 id/category（color/spacing/font/decoration/alignment 之一）\n  - [x] AC-002: describe_token('color.brand') 返回 `{ id, category, value, themeOverrides? }`\n  - [x] AC-003: Tool 实现仅调用 M-005 注册中心 API，不含业务逻辑\n- **deliverables**:\n  - [x] `apps/mcp-server/src/tools/list-tokens.ts`\n  - [x] `apps/mcp-server/src/tools/describe-token.ts`\n  - [x] `tests/mcp-server/tools/list-tokens.test.ts`\n- **relates_to**: [F-013, M-009, M-005]\n- **context_load**:\n  - arch-wechat-flow-modules#§2.M-005\n  - arch-wechat-flow-modules#§2.M-009\n\n---" .
