<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/prd/sec/3.3%20%E5%8F%AF%E9%9D%A0%E6%80%A7%E4%B8%8E%E7%A1%AE%E5%AE%9A%E6%80%A7> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/content_hash> "06b8817292ca53e5951386d0d1ab893795a907cd94007748f9f6f53709670b0c" .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/prd/sec/3.3%20%E5%8F%AF%E9%9D%A0%E6%80%A7%E4%B8%8E%E7%A1%AE%E5%AE%9A%E6%80%A7> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/position> "000009" .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/prd/sec/3.3%20%E5%8F%AF%E9%9D%A0%E6%80%A7%E4%B8%8E%E7%A1%AE%E5%AE%9A%E6%80%A7> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/narrative_body> "### 3.3 可靠性与确定性\n\n- **确定性渲染**：固定 `coreVersion + themeVersion + rulesetVersion` 下，相同 Markdown 输入必须产出 SHA-256 一致的 HTML 字节序列，不受运行时环境（浏览器主线程 / Web Worker / Node / Edge runtime）影响。\n- **跨运行时一致性**：浏览器主线程 / Web Worker / Node / Edge runtime 四运行时同输入产出字节级一致（逐字符 SHA-256 相同）。**字节级一致定义于 normalize 后产物**：LF 行尾、文档末尾单换行、行尾无尾随空白、不含 BOM；normalize 算法由 `@wechat-flow/contracts/normalizer` 单源声明，所有运行时入口统一调用。\n- **规则集回归零容忍**：过滤规则集 CI 必须 100% 通过，任何回归阻断发布。\n- **主题守护零容忍**：内置主题必须通过 9 维静态校验，任何维度不通过阻断发布。" .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/prd/sec/3.3%20%E5%8F%AF%E9%9D%A0%E6%80%A7%E4%B8%8E%E7%A1%AE%E5%AE%9A%E6%80%A7> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/Section> .
