<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/prd/sec/3.5%20%E8%A7%86%E8%A7%89%E4%B8%80%E8%87%B4%E6%80%A7%E9%AA%8C%E6%94%B6%E8%A7%84%E8%8C%83> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/section_anchor> "3.5 视觉一致性验收规范" .
