<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/ui-spec/sec/0.3%20%E5%8F%AF%E8%AE%BF%E9%97%AE%E6%80%A7%E5%9F%BA%E7%BA%BF%20%28a11y%20baseline%29> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/source_doc> "ui-spec" .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/ui-spec/sec/0.3%20%E5%8F%AF%E8%AE%BF%E9%97%AE%E6%80%A7%E5%9F%BA%E7%BA%BF%20%28a11y%20baseline%29> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/content_hash> "3e7737232b8748b92e450921ee5e81eff3a39e817e9ee253aad875c0993a93f6" .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/ui-spec/sec/0.3%20%E5%8F%AF%E8%AE%BF%E9%97%AE%E6%80%A7%E5%9F%BA%E7%BA%BF%20%28a11y%20baseline%29> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/position> "000003" .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/ui-spec/sec/0.3%20%E5%8F%AF%E8%AE%BF%E9%97%AE%E6%80%A7%E5%9F%BA%E7%BA%BF%20%28a11y%20baseline%29> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/narrative_body> "### 0.3 可访问性基线 (a11y baseline)\n\n所有组件须满足以下基线（WCAG 2.1 AA）：\n\n- **最小点击目标**：移动端 ≥ 44×44px（iOS HIG / Android Material 共识）；桌面端可缩至 32×32px\n- **焦点可见**：所有可交互元素须在键盘聚焦时显示 2px focus ring（color: `--focus-ring`）；全局通过 `:focus-visible` 启用，避免鼠标点击触发\n- **动态内容**：Toast / 状态变化 / loading 完成等动态信息使用 `aria-live=\"polite\"`；错误信息使用 `aria-live=\"assertive\"`\n- **颜色非唯一信息维度**：严重等级 / 状态等指示不得仅靠颜色区分，须配合图标或文案（如 UC-013 严重等级须色+图标双维度）\n- **对比度**：文本与背景对比度 ≥ 4.5（WCAG AA 文本基准，与 ARCH M-003/M-005 第 7 维一致）\n- **键盘操作完备**：所有鼠标可达功能须有等价键盘路径" .
