<https://cataforge.dev/instance/T-125/AC-005> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/narrative_body> "  - [ ] AC-005: Given `GET /api/v1/admin/api-keys` 已挂载，When 以合法 admin 凭据列出 API key，Then 响应状态 200，body 结构含 `keys: Array<{ keyId, name, scope, status, quotaConfig, createdAt, lastUsedAt, expiresAt, revokedAt }>` 且不含 `key` 明文字段 [ARCH#§3.API-029]" .
