<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/arch/sec/3.%20%E6%8E%A5%E5%8F%A3%E5%A5%91%E7%BA%A6> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/source_doc> "arch" .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/arch/sec/3.%20%E6%8E%A5%E5%8F%A3%E5%A5%91%E7%BA%A6> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/content_hash> "74031058d8f591fa405b69bcac9906d91b16799e956b68b505245b21ad06cd8d" .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/arch/sec/3.%20%E6%8E%A5%E5%8F%A3%E5%A5%91%E7%BA%A6> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/position> "000006" .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/arch/sec/3.%20%E6%8E%A5%E5%8F%A3%E5%A5%91%E7%BA%A6> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/narrative_body> "## 3. 接口契约\n\n接口定义见分卷 [arch-wechat-flow-api](./arch-wechat-flow-api.md)，含 API-001..API-016（合并条目）+ API-017..API-033（其中 API-033 = `describe_template`）。本主卷 frontmatter `sections_in_volumes.\"3\"` 指向该分卷。\n\n**MCP Tool 总数对账**：§3.1 共 24 个 Tool（**20 同步 + 4 异步**）= API-001..API-015（16 同步；其中 API-009 拆 `list_tokens` + `describe_token` 共 2 Tool）+ API-016 合并条目（4 异步长任务 `upload_image` / `upload_to_wechat_asset` / `export_long_image` / `export_cover` + 2 同步轮询入口 `get_job` + `get_ruleset_version`）+ API-033 `describe_template`（1 同步）+ API-034 `register_variant`（1 同步）。与 PRD §1.2.2 交付形态表的「MCP server 覆盖 24 个 Tool」字面一致。" .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/arch/sec/3.%20%E6%8E%A5%E5%8F%A3%E5%A5%91%E7%BA%A6> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/Section> .
