<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/test-report-wechat-flow/sec/1.2%20IPC%E8%BE%B9%E7%95%8C%E6%B5%8B%E8%AF%95> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/narrative_body> "### 1.2 IPC边界测试\n不适用——wechat-flow 是 Web App + npm 包 + MCP server/CLI，无桌面 IPC 层。跨进程边界（relay HTTP API、MCP stdio/HTTP transport、Worker 消息）由 `tests/relay/`、`tests/mcp-server/`、`tests/cross-runtime/worker.test.ts` 覆盖（Phase 5 产出，本轮核实仍绿）。" .
