<https://cataforge.dev/instance/T-124/AC-007> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/title> "[ ]  [ENV-LIMITATION → conditional_release]: Given 真实浏览器 Worker 环境，When 加载包含 `import` 的 plugin pack 并启动 Worker，Then `globalThis.fetch` 在 Worker 内为 `undefined`；happy-dom/jsdom 无法真实模拟 Worker `delete global`，端到端验证需 Playwright E2E 环境（T-058）" .
