<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/ui-spec/sec/1.1.2%20%E8%BE%B9%E6%A1%86%E8%89%B2%EF%BC%88Border%EF%BC%89> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/source_doc> "ui-spec" .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/ui-spec/sec/1.1.2%20%E8%BE%B9%E6%A1%86%E8%89%B2%EF%BC%88Border%EF%BC%89> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/content_hash> "322ce782c99e287750b2e86edbff2c621d480b460a1930781e528c55582b20a1" .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/ui-spec/sec/1.1.2%20%E8%BE%B9%E6%A1%86%E8%89%B2%EF%BC%88Border%EF%BC%89> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/position> "000009" .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/ui-spec/sec/1.1.2%20%E8%BE%B9%E6%A1%86%E8%89%B2%EF%BC%88Border%EF%BC%89> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/narrative_body> "#### 1.1.2 边框色（Border）\n\n| Token | 值 | 用途 |\n|-------|----|------|\n| `--color-border` | `#D9D4CB` | 标准边框（输入框、卡片轮廓） |\n| `--color-border-strong` | `#C2BCB1` | 强调边框（分隔线、选中项轮廓） |\n| `--color-border-subtle` | `#E8E4DC` | 弱化边框（仅用于区域划分，不希望边框喧宾夺主） |" .
