<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/arch/sec/API-002%3A%20lint_markdown> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/narrative_body> "#### API-002: lint_markdown\n\n```yaml\ntool: lint_markdown\nmodule: M-009\nmaps_to: F-013 AC-002\nrequest:\n  body:\n    markdown: { type: string, required: true }\n    themeId: { type: string, required: false }\nresponse:\n  schema:\n    diagnostics: { type: \"Diagnostic[]\" }\n    versionTriple: { type: \"VersionTriple\" }\n```" .
