<https://cataforge.dev/instance/T-126/AC-004> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/narrative_body> "  - [ ] AC-004: Given imageUrl SSRF 校验已实现，When `imageUrl` 为 `http://` 协议（非 https）或解析为私有 IP 段（10.x.x.x / 172.16-31.x.x / 192.168.x.x）的 URL，When 触发上传，Then 响应状态 400，body `code: 'E_SCHEMA'` 或 `'E_SSRF_BLOCKED'` [R-004 修复，ARCH#§2.M-010]" .
