<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/ui-spec/sec/1.2.1%20%E5%AD%97%E4%BD%93%E6%A0%88> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/content_hash> "45270d78ab949778d4cb23d5fa579df469092dff1ce325d54659b7b082ed3d9a" .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/ui-spec/sec/1.2.1%20%E5%AD%97%E4%BD%93%E6%A0%88> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/position> "000016" .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/ui-spec/sec/1.2.1%20%E5%AD%97%E4%BD%93%E6%A0%88> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/narrative_body> "#### 1.2.1 字体栈\n\n```css\n/* 正文衬线体（编辑器内正文、内容预览正文） */\n--font-serif: \"LXGW WenKai\", \"Source Han Serif SC\", \"Noto Serif SC\",\n              Georgia, Charter, \"Times New Roman\", serif;\n\n/* UI 无衬线体（按钮、标签、菜单、表单） */\n--font-sans: \"Inter\", system-ui, -apple-system, \"PingFang SC\",\n             \"Source Han Sans SC\", \"Noto Sans SC\", sans-serif;\n\n/* 代码等宽体（源码编辑器、内联代码、代码块） */\n--font-mono: \"JetBrains Mono\", \"Fira Code\", \"Cascadia Code\",\n             \"Source Code Pro\", ui-monospace, \"Courier New\", monospace;\n```" .
