<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/ui-spec/sec/1.1.6%20%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E8%89%B2%EF%BC%88Functional%EF%BC%89> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/content_hash> "4cb92adff255621786dc12ccf5997e927160c0c4bf9a043f78a0c16d2dc3c525" .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/ui-spec/sec/1.1.6%20%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E8%89%B2%EF%BC%88Functional%EF%BC%89> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/position> "000013" .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/ui-spec/sec/1.1.6%20%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E8%89%B2%EF%BC%88Functional%EF%BC%89> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/narrative_body> "#### 1.1.6 功能色（Functional）\n\n功能色与暖白调性协调，避免高饱和原色：\n\n| Token | 值 | 用途 |\n|-------|----|------|\n| `--color-success` | `#3A6B49` | 成功（深绿，比主题色更绿） |\n| `--color-success-subtle` | `#E6F0E9` | 成功浅底 |\n| `--color-warning` | `#8C6A1A` | 警告（暖黄棕，避免刺眼柠檬黄） |\n| `--color-warning-subtle` | `#F5EDDA` | 警告浅底 |\n| `--color-error` | `#B94A3E` | 错误（复用强调色） |\n| `--color-error-subtle` | `#F5E8E7` | 错误浅底 |\n| `--color-info` | `#3D5E8C` | 信息（偏暖的蓝灰，与暖白融合感强） |\n| `--color-info-subtle` | `#E6ECF5` | 信息浅底 |" .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/ui-spec/sec/1.1.6%20%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E8%89%B2%EF%BC%88Functional%EF%BC%89> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/Section> .
