<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/arch/sec/API-017%3A%20POST%20/api/v1/images/upload> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/content_hash> "9b362876339f1743033e1d643db87bb3c0aec5f41a4b6bf559b216a667cf43cd" .
