<https://cataforge.dev/instance/T-059/AC-001> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/title> "[x] : `validateThemeGuard(theme) → GuardResult` 保持现有契约形状 `{ passed: boolean, failures: GuardFailure[] }`（`packages/contracts/src/theme/theme-definition.ts` 中 `guardResultSchema` 不改形状）；`passed = failures.filter(f => f.severity === 'error').length === 0`；每个失败维度产出一条 `GuardFailure{ dimension: string, severity: 'error'|'warning'|'info', message?: string }`，`dimension` 字段值严格取 9 维枚举之一（见下方\"9 维守卫\"小节）[ARCH#§2.M-005]" .
